    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use one would expect from a car that has been enjoyed but never neglected. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful stewardship; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every button, switch, and gauge functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule that ensures a smooth, responsive driving experience. From the crisp engagement of the transmission to the quiet confidence of the suspension, this car is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment. It\u2019s a complete package for the discerning buyer who values both performance and presentation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
